original_title: Zara and Mike: No Nonsense Royals
overview: The Tindalls are on the surface an unlikely pairing of a Wakefield-born rugby union player and the daughter of the Princess Royal born and bred in a royal palace. This programme looks at their life together, from the highs to the lows, revealing how they carved out successful careers for themselves and supported each other along the way.
title: Zara and Mike: No Nonsense Royals
